HEADWORD: Guttle
<hw>Gut"tle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Gut</er>, <pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <def>To put into the gut; to swallow
greedily; to gorge; to gormandize.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>L'Estrange.</au> <au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
